                <span><%= eval("data.students.batch_#{batch.id}").size - 2 %> students</span> learn to <span>code & build</span> applications in Amsterdam during 12 weeks.
              </div>
              <div class='batch-item-content-btn'>
                <%= link_to 'Our students', "batches/#{batch.id}/" %>
